# Build artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/
out/

# IDE/tooling
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sln.iml
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# Package artifacts
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
